{"tid":2419084,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"多名韓星受牽連丨泫雅捲校園暴力：冇打過任何人","createTime":"2021-02-23T05:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T09:22:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af3811a864aa7d790df249475a55e40152a36f03","tid":2419084,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LyHoBzNOfDWRWEWgGIuHleG8NCU=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CR4FNBG27ZCAHDWKJHPHZVBGQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLyHoBzNOfDWRWEWgGIuHleG8NCU%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCR4FNBG27ZCAHDWKJHPHZVBGQI.jpg&h=f3f6bc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國演藝圈近日接連爆出藝人涉校園暴力事件，人氣劇《驅魔麵館》上位男星趙炳圭、女團(G)I-DLE的22歲成員穗珍後、《梨泰院Class》金東希、男團Seventeen的23歲成員珉奎、韓片《勁舞Dancing癲》26歲女星朴慧秀、前I.O.I成員金素慧等，都先後被爆是校園暴力加害者。而今日就到現年28歲的韓國「馬舞女」泫雅被爆料曾是校園暴力的加害者，有網民發文指曾遭泫雅欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：趙炳圭連環被爆涉欺凌 沉默一周首發聲：對人生產生懷疑及幻滅<br />\nIG發長文<br />\n而泫雅今日即時在IG發表長文澄清事件，表示：「出道後，受到大家的喜愛已經超過10年，現在已經14年了。對於有時過份的關注和錯誤表達，即使感到生氣，但每次都只能這樣想，這是我為了夢想而選擇的路，一笑置之就算，亦理解可能是單純的討厭我。但是每次受傷後，也不希望fans像我這樣裝作很熟悉而受傷。」泫雅強調：「我沒有打過一個耳光，也沒有打過任何人。希望寫文章的人，內心充滿幸福的事情吧。」<br />\n<br />\n朴慧秀食死貓<br />\n另外，朴慧秀昨日被爆涉嫌曾掌摑同學，甚至打電話辱罵同學父親，令她原定今日亮相KBS電台節目《鄭恩地的歌謠廣場》也無奈取消。及後網民發文更正所爆料的女藝人並非朴慧秀，令朴慧秀慘食死貓。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：韓星接連爆校園暴力爭議有原因？網民分析：將有更多黑歷史曝光<br />\n除泫雅外，男團Stray Kids成員鉉辰、女團本月少女成員Chuu都被爆是校園暴力的加害者，不過二人所屬的事務所已即時否認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3sNYfX801gpG4G2xBmci1OZDR6A=/802x1082/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CCI2DIFP45EBFCVWLCGWJXNDJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3sNYfX801gpG4G2xBmci1OZDR6A%3D%2F802x1082%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCCI2DIFP45EBFCVWLCGWJXNDJY.jpg&h=e67c3699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PJKwkeakJWb1LAFMAn8JJnL7bMw=/802x1600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TCKW2STUF5ESTD7XKPLXKMK76U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPJKwkeakJWb1LAFMAn8JJnL7bMw%3D%2F802x1600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTCKW2STUF5ESTD7XKPLXKMK76U.jpg&h=5e91d096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AW8RxyKH6dkpK-HgSpWZopStegk=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EFAJOQBARZHEXNM3FS2NDVOXHA.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAW8RxyKH6dkpK-HgSpWZopStegk%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEFAJOQBARZHEXNM3FS2NDVOXHA.jpeg&h=772420bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210223/ZQIHZBX2PNGZ7MA6HUILTMDHSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210223%2FZQIHZBX2PNGZ7MA6HUILTMDHSA%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv39B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=eb5e84fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210223%2FZQIHZBX2PNGZ7MA6HUILTMDHSA%2F&h=e56c0bc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210223/ZQIHZBX2PNGZ7MA6HUILTMDHSA/</a>"},{"pid":"bc88c08fdfb96296176e3c67d8fc7dbcd9d4dc2f","tid":2419084,"uid":153812,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"變撚到怪誕屍新娘咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fb894c6180d9548f3bfed793519abee5618f9d","tid":2419084,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"